      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent Navier-Stokes solver verified against Taylor-Couette flow analytical solution and lid-driven cavity benchmark. Convergence order confirmed at 2nd order for momentum equations. Code verification documentation provided by vendor and independently confirmed."
