      "rationale": "Experimental test matrix covers 5 flow-speed combinations: 2.5 L/min at 2000 RPM, 3.5 L/min at 2500 RPM, 5.0 L/min at 3000 RPM, 6.0 L/min at 3500 RPM, and 7.0 L/min at 4000 RPM. Fluid properties (bovine blood, 37°C, Hct 40%) documented. Test conditions replicated in CFD boundary conditions with <1% deviation in flow rate."
