      "rationale": "CFD-predicted RH index compared against experimental hemolysis measurements at all 5 operating points. Maximum deviation is 14.2% at the 7.0 L/min / 4000 RPM condition. All other conditions show deviations below 10%. Acceptance criterion of 20% is satisfied at all operating points."
    },
    {
