      "rationale": "The primary QoI is the relative hemolysis index (RH = HI_device / HI_predicate). This metric directly addresses the COU decision of identifying worst-case hemolysis conditions and comparing against the predicate device. RH < 1 acceptance criterion is consistent with FDA guidance for 510(k) hemolysis assessment."
    },
