      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry, which is the same platform as the COU device. Operating conditions span the intended CPB flow range (2.5–7.0 L/min). Blood analog fluid properties match clinical CPB conditions. Validation activities are judged sufficiently representative of the COU."
