    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2. CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions under CPB use. Experimental validation dataset (dataVintage 2025-10-08) predates the current model revision (2026-02-15); re-validation against the updated model build is planned for the next assessment cycle. Current evidence is considered sufficient for the Medium assurance level at MRL 2.",
